title: lmao actually managed to lose in a bronze game
body:
80k damage dealt to champions, 360 thousand damage dealt overall, 28/8, 6 turrets and inhib taken by myself, team is 0/11 0/11 0/8 1/12 i'm 28/8 LMAO i now understand what doublelift meant when he said some games cannot be carried, 

until this point i didn't think you could lose in bronze as a player in plat/diamond
